> [!INFO]
> category of artificial intelligence that involves **training models on unlabeled data**

- allowing model to **identify patterns**, **structures**, and **relationships without explicit guidance**
- operates **autonomously**
- primary techniques
	- [[Summary of Unsupervised Learning#Clustering|Clustering]]: group similar data points
	- [[Summary of Unsupervised Learning#Association Rule Learning|Association Rule]]: discovering relationships between variables
	- [[Summary of Unsupervised Learning#Dimensionality Reduction|Dimensionality Reduction]]: help simplify complex datasets by reducing the number of variables
# Purpose

- to discover **underlying patterns within data without predefined labels or targe outcomes**
# Benefits

- ability to **analyze vast amounts of unstructured data efficiently**
- models are **highly adaptable**
	- can uncover trends in real-time
	- require less human intervention
- facilitate data-driven decision-making
	- identify key relationships within datasets
- enhances feature engineering
	- improve performance of other machine learning models by **identifying the most relevant variables**
